        Selling a Queenslander or Character Home in Brisbane
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Queenslanders and character homes sell differently from modern properties. Here's how they are valued, who buys them, and how to present one for maximum result.
      </p>
